<inglise>(4) Section 151 (5) is added to the Criminal Code (RT 1992, 20, 288; 1997, 21/22, 353; 87, 1468; 1998, 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 412; 36/37, 553; 51, 756, 759; 59, 941; 98/99, 1576; 107, 1766; 108/109, 1783; 1999, 4, 53; 10, 156; 16, 267; 16, 271; 16, 276; 26, 377; 29, 398; 57, 595; 57, 597; 57, 598; 60, 616; 97, 859; 102, 907; 2000, 10, 55; 28, 167; 29, 173; 33, 193; 40, 247; 49, 301; 49, 305; 54, 351; 57, 373; 58, 376; 84, 533; 92, 597) worded as follows: </inglise>


<eesti>(1) Riigireservi omavolilise kasutamise eest, kui sellega p&otilde;hjustati oluline kahju v&otilde;i kui s&uuml;&uuml;dlase suhtes oli samasuguse rikkumise eest kohaldatud distsiplinaar- v&otilde;i halduskaristust, - karistatakse rahatrahviga v&otilde;i arestiga. </eesti>
<inglise>Unlawful use of national stockpiles (1) Unauthorised use of national stockpiles, if significant damage is caused thereby or if a disciplinary or administrative punishment has been imposed on the offender for a similar offence, is punishable by a fine or detention. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sama teo eest, kui sellega p&otilde;hjustati suur kahju v&otilde;i muu raske tagaj&auml;rg - karistatakse rahatrahviga v&otilde;i arestiga v&otilde;i vabadusekaotusega kuni viie aastani." </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Same act, if it causes major damage or other serious consequences, is punishable by a fine or detention or imprisonment for up to five years." </inglise>
